We have tried this and looks like we can pass the `correlation_id` as part of the "headers" and it will come as part of request header for webhook.
@norman.leitman we can share the example body as below for Liz reference.
```{
    "batch_id": "<batch_id>",
    "settings":{
        "webhook_config":{
            "url": "<URL>",
            "headers": {"correlation_id":"Test12345"}
        }
    }
}```
